<title>RUSSIA: Three Russians die in helicopter crash.</title>
<headline>Three Russians die in helicopter crash.</headline>
<dateline>MOSCOW 1997-04-03</dateline>
<text>
<p>Three people were killed and two injured on Thursday when a passenger helicopter from the local medical service crashed in Russia's Perm region in the Urals, a spokeswoman for the emergencies ministry said.</p>
<p>The Mi-8 helicopter hit a radio mast on take-off, burst into flames and crashed. Two survivors were rushed to hospital, she said.</p>
